
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-gray-mpls-tp-nm-req-03.txt'>
    <title>"MPLS TP Network Management Requirements", Scott Mansfield, Kam Lam, Eric  Gray</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-gray-mpls-tp-nm-req-03.txt</link>
    <description>This document specifies the requirements necessary to manage the  elements and networks that support an MPLS Transport Profile  (MPLS-TP). This document is a product of a joint International  Telecommunications Union - Telecommunications Standardization  Sector (ITU-T) and Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF) effort  to include a MPLS Transport Profile within the IETF MPLS  architecture. The requirements are driven by the management  functionality needs defined by ITU-T for packet transport  networks.  Gray, et al  Expires August, 2009  [page 1]  Internet-Draft  MPLS-TP NM Requirements  February, 2009</description>
    <dc:date>2009-02-05T23:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
